<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>태양광 모니터링 - 모드 설정</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.10.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/animate/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.carousel.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.theme.default.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #6a11cb;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .navbar .team-name {
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .right-nav {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logout-btn {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border: 2px solid #17a2b8; /* 민트색 테두리 */
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #6a11cb; /* 네비게이션 바 색상 */
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover {
            background-color: #5c0db6; /* 마우스 오버 시 약간 더 어두운 색 */
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .mode-section {
            width: 48%;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .mode-section img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .mode-button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: none;
            background: #17a2b8;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="team-name">ANS</div>
        <a href="/dashboard">발전량 통계</a>
        <a href="/forecast">발전량 예측</a>
        <a href="/mode">모드</a>
        <a href="/trade">전력 거래</a>
        <a href="/news">기술 소식</a>
    
        <div class="right-nav">
            <span><%= userNickname %>님 환영합니다!</span>
            <a href="/user/logout" class="logout-btn">로그아웃</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="container">
        <div class="mode-section">
            <h2>스노우 모드</h2>
            <p>스노우 모드는 눈이 많이 올 때 패널에 눈이 쌓이지 않도록 경사각을 조정하여 최적의 발전 효율을 유지하는 모드입니다.</p>
            <img src="/image/screenshot-1.png" alt="스노우 모드">
            <button class="mode-button" onclick="activateSnowMode()">스노우 모드 활성화</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mode-section">
            <h2>윈드 모드</h2>
            <p>윈드 모드는 강풍이 불 때 패널의 각도를 조정하여 바람의 저항을 최소화하고 안전성을 높이는 모드입니다.</p>
            <img src="/image/screenshot-2.png" alt="윈드 모드">
            <button class="mode-button" onclick="activateWindMode()">윈드 모드 활성화</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/lib/owlcarousel/owl.carousel.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        function activateSnowMode() {
            fetch('/run-snow-mode')
                .then(response => response.text())
                .then(data => alert(data))
                .catch(error => console.error('Error:', error));
        }

        function activateWindMode() {
            fetch('/run-wind-mode')
                .then(response => response.text())
                .then(data => alert(data))
                .catch(error => alert('Error activating Wind Mode: ' + error));
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
